{"tid":881833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李斯特城空難死者身份曝光　泰國環姐香消玉殞　機師情侶雙雙斃命","createTime":"2018-10-29T17:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T11:19:14.000Z","uid":117200,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"207863b427d66d62335a929e2351e6f49e3eb335","tid":881833,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:30:43.000Z","msg":"英超球會李斯特城（Leicester City）班主維猜（Vichai Srivaddhanaprabha）周六（27日）觀看完球隊比賽後，由球場乘坐直升機離開時發生意外，機上5人不幸罹難。當局公布死者身份，除了維猜外，亦包括曾經參加泰國選美的助手，以及是飛行經驗老到的情侶檔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2026850/org/f5825e0bcbc68686a93f67e4cf22b65e.jpg/92mcwxFT7Ki8l7xox2lhQBY6R7aoZdJBmPFPwpjxT8I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2026850%2Forg%2Ff5825e0bcbc68686a93f67e4cf22b65e.jpg%2F92mcwxFT7Ki8l7xox2lhQBY6R7aoZdJBmPFPwpjxT8I&h=5c3effb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n33歲的Nursara Suknamai是維猜的其中一位助手，不時隨對方到李斯特城主場王權球場（King Power Stadium）欣賞球隊比賽，但原來這位美女助手的背景並不簡單。她曾經在2005年出戰環球小姐（Miss Universe）泰國代表選舉，即使最終以第3名完成，但贏得「最上鏡小姐」榮譽。事實上，她經常在社交媒體公開自己的工作和生活照，足跡遍布歐亞多國。<br />\n<br />\n另外她亦喜歡健身，因此在她的Instagram不時見到她在健身室或鍛鍊瑜伽的片段。而Nursara最後的照片是在上周四（25日）公開，是一張微笑的自拍相。縱觀她超過2800張照片，大部分都見到她臉帶笑臉的樣子，充滿陽光氣息，可惜一切已成絕響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2026774/org/040a9fd0cb4786f00a2ac51a0a1551b1.jpg/_21-otg_cqqpeSJXjnsK8DmZfuhQX_nSXyu2YF8rtmA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2026774%2Forg%2F040a9fd0cb4786f00a2ac51a0a1551b1.jpg%2F_21-otg_cqqpeSJXjnsK8DmZfuhQX_nSXyu2YF8rtmA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=3561426e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外奮力將失控直升機飛至空曠地方墜毀的機師斯沃弗（Eric Swaffer）雖然犧牲性命，但亦因為這個舉動而避免造成更多傷亡。終年56歲的斯沃弗是一位擁有超過20年飛行經驗的高手，亦是歐洲聯合航空機構JAA（Joint Aviation Authorities）的教官和考官，證明他在飛行界是位老行尊。<br />\n<br />\n而在今次意外中喪生的46歲女乘客萊霍維奇（Izabela Roza Lechowicz）其實是斯沃弗的伴侶，對方亦是一位機師，因此他們在工作內外的關係都非常親密。萊霍維奇出生於波蘭，在1997年移居英國。對於她的離世，波蘭駐英國大使館發表聲明，大讚她是一位偉大的機師，並成為100位居英波蘭女性之冠，肯定她為國家推動正面形象的貢獻。"},{"pid":"e1328bd7e563f9d271a889dc38233895b5de8cc4","tid":881833,"uid":117200,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/30/PwH3m5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2FPwH3m5.jpg&h=f1a72491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/30/Z23zDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2FZ23zDQ.jpg&h=a667e133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/30/UxwC9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2FUxwC9y.jpg&h=824bf569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/30/c1EeZo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2Fc1EeZo.jpg&h=65624e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/30/bn8jiT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2Fbn8jiT.jpg&h=fdbda5c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/30/oIA98f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2FoIA98f.jpg&h=a3b5a7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/30/QRzleb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2FQRzleb.jpg&h=70812623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/30/LV7qK8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2FLV7qK8.jpg&h=c1f53377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/30/tUAn26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2FtUAn26.jpg&h=62a9faac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />